ey armed? ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 63436, "End": 63528}, {"Reply": "They're hiding, I bet. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 65206, "End": 65229}, {"Reply": "You keep an eye on him, Mace!  You watch him! ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 66123, "End": 66189}, {"Reply": "First off, if there's one, there's more.  That's how it is, soldiers travel in bunches.  Second, they don't waste soldiers on folks like us, that's for police!  Training soldiers to kill weaklings like us is not what they call \"cost effective.\" ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 79558, "End": 79943}, {"Reply": "Other soldiers!  There's a saying, \"Soldiers deserve soldiers.\" ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 80093, "End": 80177}, {"Reply": "I don't see how you can not remember how you got here, Sergeant. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 80895, "End": 80980}, {"Reply": "Then how come you're not with your unit? ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 81640, "End": 81701}, {"Reply": "It's not an unreasonable question. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 81866, "End": 81901}, {"Reply": " How about it, Sergeant? ", "Didascalie": "(to Todd)", "Start": 81935, "End": 81980}, {"Reply": "That's good news, you think? ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 205983, "End": 206012}, {"Reply": "army?  Couldn't if he wanted. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 206273, "End": 206303}, {"Reply": "care about us, he's a soldier.  Besides, we threw him out, remember? ", "Didascalie": "(grunt)", "Start": 206657, "End": 206765}, {"Reply": "There's soldiers coming. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 211062, "End": 211087}, {"Reply": "You know where Thomas keeps those two axes?  Go get the axes. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 212777, "End": 212858}, {"Reply": "as fighting. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 213221, "End": 213234}, {"Reply": "work.  Where's them axes?  He musta run into soldiers and got killed. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 216160, "End": 216249}, {"Reply": "they start -- unless you stop 'em. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 216470, "End": 216505}, {"Reply": " Only one axe? ", "Didascalie": "(grabbing the axe)", "Start": 216972, "End": 217006}, {"Reply": " Toldja. ", "Didascalie": "(chopping furiously)", "Start": 217177, "End": 217205}, {"Reply": " More!  Trust me! ", "Didascalie": "(chopping)", "Start": 217561, "End": 217598}, {"Reply": "Do what you can. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 217865, "End": 217882}, {"Reply": "They're gonna kill us anyhow.  No point in surrendering. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 218007, "End": 218083}, {"Reply": " Turn! ", "Didascalie": "(grabbing the axe)", "Start": 218126, "End": 218152}, {"Reply": "You! ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 235679, "End": 235684}, {"Reply": "Well then, I guess you fellas are all right.  I guess I misjudged you some.  Where I said you were \"a buncha no good killer robots,\" I mighta just overspoke myself.  As of now, till it goes otherwise, you got my sincere approval and support. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 249662, "End": 250024}]}, {"Character": "ELISE", "Replies": [{"Reply": "How could there only be one?  How could he get here? ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 64184, "End": 64257}]}, {"Character": "MACE", "Replies": [{"Reply": "He was unconscious.  We couldn't ask him anything.  He -- ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 64397, "End": 64475}, {"Reply": "What do you mean he's survived worse?  Did he say something? ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 68120, "End": 68201}, {"Reply": " A soldier! ", "Didascalie": "(worried)", "Start": 68472, "End": 68504}, {"Reply": " Where's Nathan? ", "Didascalie": "(suddenly alarmed)", "Start": 69090, "End": 69127}, {"Reply": "If there's any danger to Nathan -- ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 69429, "End": 69464}, {"Reply": "We're teaching the boy to walk. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 71921, "End": 71953}, {"Reply": "I got something for you. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 72461, "End": 72486}, {"Reply": "Here. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 72660, "End": 72666}, {"Reply": "Like this. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 72757, "End": 72768}, {"Reply": "See? ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 72880, "End": 72885}, {"Reply": "Practice with it.  In a day or two maybe you'll be strong enough to go out to the garden with Sandra. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 72995, "End": 73137}, {"Reply": "Let's go.  Come on, Sergeant. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 74973, "End": 75003}, {"Reply": "Replaced? ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 82217, "End": 82227}, {"Reply": " That's why we're weighing down.  And that's why we're always on the wire even when the wind's down, like now. ", "Didascalie": "(continuing)", "Start": 89731, "End": 89902}, {"Reply": "Oh, we're not going to shoot anything.  That's not what we mean by \"hunting.\" ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 90612, "End": 90730}, {"Reply": " Jimmy Pig, you're not going to shoot anything, are you? ", "Didascalie": "(then, laughing, to Jimmy Pig)", "Start": 90811, "End": 90908}, {"Reply": " It's how we call for help.  Two shots.  There'll be someone on duty, listening in case we get off the wire and get lost or something.  We have flares too.  Come on. ", "Didascalie": "(to Todd)", "Start": 91103, "End": 91369}, {"Reply": "Sandra said she told you how we wound up here.  Our parents and so on. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 91974, "End": 92085}, {"Reply": " Over here, we call these \"catcher trenches.\" ", "Didascalie": "(turning left, indicating)", "Start": 92162, "End": 92248}, {"Reply": " Smaller stuff that blows across the ground, it falls in these trenches, it works sort of like a filter.  We go through the trenches sometimes and get some good stuff. ", "Didascalie": "(continuing)", "Start": 92412, "End": 92680}, {"Reply": "We try to work 'em when they're dry. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 92950, "End": 92987}, {"Reply": "Whatever looks useful, if we can get a rope to it, we'll go for it.  But you can't ever go further than your safety line because it'll come up on you with sometimes maybe ten seconds or even less. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 93528, "End": 93825}, {"Reply": "Like right now.  You hear that? ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 93997, "End": 94029}, {"Reply": "It's close when you hear that. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 94244, "End": 94275}, {"Reply": "SHE'S GONNA BLOW, JIMMY. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 94538, "End": 94563}, {"Reply": "GRAB ON, SERGEANT! ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 94864, "End": 94883}, {"Reply": "Dumpers.  They come every twenty or thirty days. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 98142, "End": 98211}, {"Reply": "There's going to be a meeting. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 121867, "End": 121898}, {"Reply": "That's what scares people.  He gets stronger every day. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 122093, "End": 122168}, {"Reply": "I've caught him..sneaking looks at you.  At your body. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 122375, "End": 122449}, {"Reply": "Yes. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 122769, "End": 122774}, {"Reply": "Maybe he is.  It doesn't matter. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 123327, "End": 123360}, {"Reply": "We'll give you any tools you need, warm clothing, a good knife, boots. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 129173, "End": 129263}, {"Reply": "We voted wrong! ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 140305, "End": 140321}, {"Reply": "TODD!  TODD! ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 143601, "End": 143614}, {"Reply": " TODD!  WE WANT YOU TO COME BACK!  WE MADE A MISTAKE! ", "Didascalie": "(pauses, then)", "Start": 143653, "End": 143745}, {"Reply": "TODD!  WE'RE SORRY!  WE WERE WRONG! ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 144012, "End": 144048}, {"Reply": "Damn!  Thank you, Todd.  God damn! ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 144522, "End": 144557}, {"Reply": "Look at that.  It's some kind of vehicle.  A landing party.  HEY! ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 145958, "End": 146043}, {"Reply": "Why?  Why? ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 150300, "End": 150311}, {"Reply": "I'm not..a soldier. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 150388, "End": 150408}]}, {"Character": "JIMMY PIG", "Replies": [{"Reply": "Oh, come on, Slade, let the man eat. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 81767, "End": 81804}, {"Reply": " What could I hit? ", "Didascalie": "(laughing)", "Start": 90989, "End": 91028}, {"Reply": "Thanks, partner.  These no-goods woulda just let me blow away. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 98777, "End": 98860}, {"Reply": "HO HO HO!  HO HO HO! ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 106999, "End": 107020}, {"Reply": "He saved my life out there.  I guess Mace told you. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 117929, "End": 118000}, {"Reply": "Scarf!  Scarf! ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 120256, "End": 120271}, {"Reply": "GOTCHA! ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 197829, "End": 197837}, {"Reply": "Johnny, get over under that table with Miss Sandra and Ellen and the others.  Miss Judith, you better go on down the root cellar with Emma and help with the ones down there. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 198639, "End": 198889}, {"Reply": " Give us a hand, dammit! ", "Didascalie": "(to Red)", "Start": 205606, "End": 205650}, {"Reply": "Don't worry.  Couple more inches and they're out. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 211432, "End": 211501}, {"Reply": "don't have time. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 213088, "End": 213105}, {"Reply": "How do you know there's soldiers coming? ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 216314, "End": 216355}, {"Reply": " How many? ", "Didascalie": "(to Red)", "Start": 217284, "End": 217314}, {"Reply": " Turns. ", "Didascalie": "(grabbing the axe)", "Start": 217687, "End": 217714}, {"Reply": "Thank God! ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 235750, "End": 235761}]}, {"Character": "SANDRA", "Replies": [{"Reply": "Want to try some more of this? ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 67199, "End": 67230}, {"Reply": "You rest now.  I'll give you more later. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 67376, "End": 67437}, {"Reply": "No, but he's covered with old wounds, all sorts of scars.  Knife scars, bullet scars, burns. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 68264, "End": 68397}, {"Reply": "There are words on his shoulder. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 68567, "End": 68600}, {"Reply": "We'll have to sleep on the floor. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 68972, "End": 69006}, {"Reply": " I won't permit danger to Nathan. ", "Didascalie": "(interrupting grimly)", "Start": 69553, "End": 69607}, {"Reply": " He's late learning.  He was sick for a long time. ", "Didascalie": "(nervously filling silence)", "Start": 72048, "End": 72139}, {"Reply": "You have to watch out for them. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 77147, "End": 77179}, {"Reply": "In a month this one will be as big as those. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 77608, "End": 77673}, {"Reply": "Here.  You try one. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 78153, "End": 78173}, {"Reply": "So there really wasn't any choice. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 85746, "End": 85781}, {"Reply": "I guess that's what you like!  The fighting, I mean.  The wars. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 86580, "End": 86664}, {"Reply": "We'll eat these. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 110957, "End": 110974}, {"Reply": " Well, not quite an expert. ", "Didascalie": "(a laugh)", "Start": 111732, "End": 111780}, {"Reply": "What do you think about? ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 112596, "End": 112621}, {"Reply": "Do you think about food?  Or women? ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 112710, "End": 112746}, {"Reply": "What about feelings then?  You must have feelings.  You must feel something. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 112922, "End": 113039}, {"Reply": " Now? ", "Didascalie": "(amazed)", "Start": 113765, "End": 113791}, {"Reply": " Oh, my God.  But there's nothing to be afraid of here.  I can't hurt you.  I wouldn't. ", "Didascalie": "(growing horror)", "Start": 114335, "End": 114483}, {"Reply": "It's beautiful, Jimmy.  He'll love it. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 117754, "End": 117812}, {"Reply": " You should give it to him yourself. ", "Didascalie": "(nods)", "Start": 118074, "End": 118130}, {"Reply": "He's not fully recovered. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 122007, "End": 122033}, {"Reply": "I know. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 122511, "End": 122519}, {"Reply": "Are you afraid of him, Mace? ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 122612, "End": 122641}, {"Reply": "He told me he's afraid. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 123243, "End": 123267}, {"Reply": "What happened? ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 126659, "End": 126674}, {"Reply": "Mace!  What about the vote? ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 140070, "End": 140098}, {"Reply": "What's going on? ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 145407, "End": 145424}, {"Reply": "Keep going, children, don't panic, don't panic. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 159197, "End": 159264}, {"Reply": "Into the bedroom, all of you. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 163263, "End": 163293}, {"Reply": "Sergeant Todd! ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 164395, "End": 164410}, {"Reply": "Did he find you? ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 173316, "End": 173333}, {"Reply": "How do you know they'll come back? ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 175324, "End": 175359}, {"Reply": "Nothing? ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 175726, "End": 175735}, {"Reply": "You know who they are, don't you? ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 175969, "End": 176003}, {"Reply": "Seventeen!  My God! ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 176284, "End": 176304}, {"Reply": " You can't fight seventeen yourself! ", "Didascalie": "(suddenly energized)", "Start": 176349, "End": 176405}, {"Reply": "Why not? ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 177004, "End": 177013}, {"Reply": "Sergeant!  Sergeant Todd! ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 181584, "End": 181610}, {"Reply": "He's not dead! ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 206919, "End": 206934}, {"Reply": " SHHHHHHH! ", "Didascalie": "(suddenly, urgently)", "Start": 219026, "End": 219056}, {"Reply": "Go? ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 220006, "End": 220010}, {"Reply": "Sarah, you hang on to Sergeant Todd. ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 221623, "End": 221660}, {"Reply": "Ellen, go to the Commons.  Tell Jimmy Pig and Mr. Slade that Sergeant Todd says we have to leave as soon as they get everybody out of the root-cellar.  Can you do that? ", "Didascalie": "", "Start": 221891, "End": 22213